text: evaraite cinna cinna tappulu tappa, pedda papala nundi mariyu asahyakaramaina panula nundi duranga untaro vari koraku, niscayanga, ni prabhuvu ksamapana paridhi cala visalamainadi. Mim'malni matti nundi srstincinappati nundi mariyu mi tallula garbhalalo pindaluga unnappati nundi kuda, ayanaku mi gurinci baga telusu. Kavuna miru mi pavitratanu gurinci (goppalu) ceppukokandi. Evadu bhayabhaktulu galavado ayanaku baga telusu
